ttp://hybridauth.sourceforge.net/userguide/Configuration.html).\n4. Now you can run snippet [[!HybriAuth?providers=`Twitter`]] on any page.\n\nIf there will be any errors on library initialization - it will be logged in in system log.\n\nI recorded simple video with Twitter login http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ron_VTaQeWE for you.\";}', 'HybridAuth', null, '1', '1', '4', 'pl', '0');
